487 Chat App

How to Run:

- On your terminal run: python3 main.py

Before Running:

- Make sure Netcat exists at '/usr/bin/nc'.
- If you want to use Netcat at a different location, change 'NC' variable at the top of main.py
- Default port for communication is 12487, you can change 'PORT' variable at the top of main.py
- This app uses only built in Python libraries so there is no requirements.txt included.

Usage

- Enter a username when asked.
- '\discover' to find users.
- Type a username to open chat.
- '\menu' to return, '\quit' to exit.
